title: Looking for a Premade team for Onslaught QUEST!
body:
HELLO.

I am looking for a premade team for Onslaught quest currently. I am able to play only Lulu ( AD/Sup ), Lux ( AP/Sup), Ahri (AP) and probably Soraka and janna as a supporter. If you are still looking for someone to finish the quest, PLZ add me on your friendlist.

Dunphy
